---
import Hero from "@/common/components/Hero.astro";
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import ChevronRightIcon from "@heroicons/react/24/solid/ChevronRightIcon";
---

<BaseLayout title="Graduate">
	<Hero title="Graduate" />

	<main class="mb-20 mt-10 space-y-10">
		<section class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl px-5">
			<p class="font-sarabun">
				For those seeking to deepen their academic pursuits and contribute to the advancement of knowledge in
				mathematics and computer science, the Department of Mathematics and Computer Science at Chulalongkorn
				University offers a range of rigorous graduate programs. Our programs cater to individuals with a strong
				foundation in mathematics or computer science, providing opportunities to specialize in diverse areas of
				study. Whether your passion lies in exploring theoretical mathematics, applying mathematical principles
				to solve real-world problems, or delving into the intricacies of computer science and information
				technology, our graduate programs offer a stimulating academic environment for intellectual growth and
				professional development. Join our community of scholars and benefit from the expertise of our renowned
				faculty as you embark on a journey of research, innovation, and academic excellence.
			</p>
		</section>

		<section class="mx-auto max-w-screen-xl space-y-5 px-5">
			<h2 class="font-kanit text-5xl font-semibold">Our Graduate Programs</h2>
			<div class="grid gap-5 md:grid-cols-3">
				<article class="bg-slate-800 text-white shadow-lg">
					<img src="/placeholder.jpeg" alt="" class="brightness-75 filter" />
					<div class="flex h-full flex-col justify-between space-y-2.5 p-5">
						<div>
							<h3 class="mb-2.5 font-kanit text-3xl font-medium">Mathematics</h3>
							<p class="font-sm font-sarabun font-light">
								Advance your mathematical knowledge and research skills, exploring pure and applied
								mathematics for a career in academia or research.
							</p>
						</div>
						<a href="/graduate/mathematics" class="flex items-center font-kanit text-yellow-500"
							>Learn more <ChevronRightIcon className="h-4 w-4" /></a
						>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="bg-slate-800 text-white shadow-lg">
					<div class="flex h-full flex-col justify-between space-y-2.5 p-5">
						<div>
							<h3 class="mb-2.5 font-kanit text-3xl font-medium">
								Applied Mathematics & Computational Science
							</h3>
							<p class="font-sm font-sarabun font-light">
								Harness the power of mathematics and computing to solve real-world problems across
								science and engineering disciplines.
							</p>
						</div>
						<a href="/graduate/amcs" class="flex items-center font-kanit text-yellow-500"
							>Learn more <ChevronRightIcon className="h-4 w-4" /></a
						>
					</div>
				</article>
				<article class="bg-slate-800 text-white shadow-lg">
					<div class="flex h-full flex-col justify-between space-y-2.5 p-5">
						<div>
							<h3 class="mb-2.5 font-kanit text-3xl font-medium">
								Computer Science and Information Technology
							</h3>
							<p class="font-sm font-sarabun font-light">
								AI Explore cutting-edge topics in computer science and information technology,
								specializing in areas like AI, data science, and cybersecurity.
							</p>
						</div>
						<div class="flex space-x-10">
							<a href="/graduate/csit" class="flex items-center font-kanit text-yellow-500"
								>Learn more <ChevronRightIcon className="h-4 w-4" /></a
							>
						</div>
					</div>
				</article>
			</div>
		</section>
	</main>
</BaseLayout>
